<plot>Follow this pair of "Indie" filmmakers, Beaux Kristoffer and D'aria Magento, as they try to get one of their creations into a film festival - any film festival. Clips from their previous work are included as they embark on creating a new film in the never-ending circle that is filmmaking. In the great tradition of "Project Greenlight" and "Waiting for Guffman", meet Beaux &amp; D'aria.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?062674</url></doc>
